# ERVI Group server

**Backend service** for managing and tracking delivery orders.  
Built with **Node.js + Express + Prisma**, this API handles everything from **order creation** to **email notifications** and **PDF invoice generation**.

---

## Features

- **Authentication & Authorization** – JWT (Access + Refresh tokens)
- **Order Management** – create, update, and list delivery orders
- **Email Notifications** – powered by [Resend](https://resend.com)
- **PDF Generation** – dynamic delivery documents / invoices
- **Route detection** – based on receiver’s country
- **Environment-aware deployment** – Railway / Render / Vercel ready

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-------------|
| **Runtime** | Node.js |
| **Framework** | Express |
| **Database ORM** | Prisma |
| **Email Provider** | Resend API |
| **Auth Tokens** | JWT (Access + Refresh) |
| **PDF Engine** | pdfkit / pdf-lib |
| **Deployment** | Railway |
